        "text": "Matthew 3:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") denied (as materialists, perhaps holding the theory of emanations) that there were angels and spirit-beings, i.e. independent spiritual realities besides God. To this category of ",
        "children": []
      },
